      "span_text": "Honeycombing with emphysematous destruction was observed in half of the CPFE patients, with enlargement and sometimes thinning of the walls, which also composes the UIP pattern, indicating a pathological characteristic of CPFE. Honeycombing with thin walls and enlargement have previously been observed in CPFE patients  , and we also noted these findings in our patients.",
